parameters: \N<Kazumi>Have you decided on the plan to revitalize the village?
\N<Kazumi>Hey! Hikaru! Don't run around inside the house!!

\N<Kazumi>Yeah, that person has been acting strange lately! Not even
putting Hikaru to bed.
\N<Kazumi>I have to scold him again...! Ahaha.

\N<Kazumi>Ah, it seems like I can't leave right now, so please wait
outside...!
\N<Kazumi>I'm sorry - you came all this way for nothing!
\N<Kazumi>What's wrong? On a night like this.
\N<Naoto>Ah, it's about the village revitalization project....

\N<Kazumi>We have to come up with a plan for it again this year, huh?
Haha.

\N<Naoto>If I remember correctly, Kazumi-san came up with a plan last
year.
\N<Kazumi>I see... So you came here for that?
\N<Kazumi>Well, it's a bit of a hassle, isn't it? Haha.
\N<Naoto>More than it being a hassle, I just don't know what to do....

\N<Kazumi>It's fine to just come up with something random, right? Just
come up with something random and laugh.

\N<Kazumi>Is that so? There's no need to think so hard about it, just
laugh it off.

\N<Kazumi>Bringing people into this remote village itself is a crazy
idea, so just laugh it off.
\N<Kaede>The village chief is saying the same thing....

\N<Kazumi>Yeah. We reduced the accommodation fees at the inn in the
village by half.
\N<Kazumi>That's all. Well, it didn't have any effect though - haha.
\N<Naoto>Oh, speaking of which, what about Yosuke-san?
\N<Kazumi>I'm putting Hikaru to bed right now.

\N<Naoto>Alright, I'll save the discussion about Yosuke-san for
another time.
\N<Kazumi>Sorry, my child has trouble falling asleep...haha.
\N<Naoto>Well then, I apologize for coming so late at night.
\N<Naoto>Huh, I wonder if they're not home.... But the door was open.
\N<Naoto>...Oh well. I guess I'll go home.

\N<Naoto>Ah, Yosuke-san didn't reply so I thought I'd just... wait,
huh!?

\N<Kazumi>W-Well, it's not a big deal... What's wrong? Why are you
here so late at night?
\N<Naoto>Um, well... Yosuke-san called me, so I came here.
\N<Kazumi>Huh!? If it's Yosuke, he's actually out right now....
It's not good to just barge in without permission...
\N<Naoto>Huh, I wonder if they're not home.... But the door was open.
\N<Naoto>...Oh well. I guess I'll go home.
